  portage set, bug #440904.

*smart-live-rebuild-1.2.4 (31 Oct 2012)

  31 Oct 2012; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
  +smart-live-rebuild-1.2.4.ebuild:
  Version bump. The new version adds a --quiet option, disables creating binary
  packages with --pretend and fixes an attempt to kill dead child process.

